      "List, search, filter, and inspect available inference.sh apps.",
      "Run cloud apps with inline input or saved input files.",
      "Generate sample app input files before execution.",
      "Track task status and save task results after long-running jobs.",
      "Use supported apps for images, videos, audio, text, search, 3D, and Twitter/X actions."
